        <updateDate>2021-04-21T18:21:27Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Students Before Unions Act</strong></p> <p>This bill requires local educational agencies, as a condition of receiving certain elementary and secondary school emergency relief subgrants, to publicly disclose negotiations with labor organizations (e.g., teacher unions) that are related to providing in-person instruction.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
